{"tid":774781,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實啲hyperinflation國家將啲銀紙減少幾個零有咩意義","createTime":"2018-08-10T15:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T02:06:40.000Z","uid":164920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"164e0e6ca97fa64393672c8bd98ec24c560bd95c","tid":774781,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T15:03:04.000Z","msg":"根據mv=py，如果一個國家實際output唔增加，根本就無改變到&ldquo;錢賤貨貴&rdquo;既局面。單純將銀紙面額減幾個零有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e83f469d398e9e7f7cecba50f5b96402d37da4","tid":774781,"uid":132859,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T15:08:58.000Z","msg":"等人去買嘢食嗰陣可以抬多啲銀紙囉"},{"pid":"d698b070e74c7aaa2e43af02e474e08bfaffde97","tid":774781,"uid":1524,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T15:43:46.000Z","msg":"容易D計數，唔洗等你下下都要加減乘除一千幾百萬先知結果。"},{"pid":"50b2968162a71e764afedeba26164e7d455e047b","tid":774781,"uid":192460,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"164e0e6ca97fa64393672c8bd98ec24c560bd95c","tid":774781,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T15:03:04.000Z","msg":"根據mv=py，如果一個國家實際output唔增加，根本就無改變到&ldquo;錢賤貨貴&rdquo;既局面。單純將銀紙面額減幾個零有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:50:19.000Z","msg":"hyperinflation 真係好難搞<br />\n<br />\n毫無疑問，原因係由於M增長過度。要解決問題，理所當然係要減少M嘅增長率。但實際操作上好難，因為政府之所以要增加money supply，明顯係因為government 支出過大，要靠印銀紙去比錢<br />\n<br />\n所以，重點要轉移去財政政策<br />\n<br />\n要減少government deficit，就要減少支出。但係咁做會做成production 減少。根據Phillips curve，減少inflation rate會造成unemployment rate上升，即係從一舊屎去另一舊屎<br />\n<br />\n係咁嘅情況下，output增長唔到<br />\n<br />\n政府能夠做嘅，就好似1985年嘅玻利維亞，政府<span style=\"color: red;\">每日</span>都量入為出。繼續搞貨幣簡直晒氣<br />\n<br />\n寫paper寫到頭痛，sorry for 1999<br />\n<br />\n歡迎深入理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：經濟金融系grad"},{"pid":"08e5d4379aa81252b737f11c11124b79a2736e6a","tid":774781,"uid":180156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:33:27.000Z","msg":"呢d國家直比強國做殖民地算喇"},{"pid":"7df328199b97c7c951506f3024cce8bbfb206eea","tid":774781,"uid":33213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08e5d4379aa81252b737f11c11124b79a2736e6a","tid":774781,"uid":180156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:33:27.000Z","msg":"呢d國家直比強國做殖民地算喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:43:48.000Z","msg":"hyperinflation好多強國都出現過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780cec5aaebe99b3e297c6f6315a8881bbe94fdf","tid":774781,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7df328199b97c7c951506f3024cce8bbfb206eea","tid":774781,"uid":33213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08e5d4379aa81252b737f11c11124b79a2736e6a","tid":774781,"uid":180156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:33:27.000Z","msg":"呢d國家直比強國做殖民地算喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:43:48.000Z","msg":"hyperinflation好多強國都出現過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T14:04:50.000Z","msg":"有無例子?"},{"pid":"30b031f0d0fd8e5c3e0ba683b50e23ffafe5ea80","tid":774781,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T14:09:02.000Z","msg":"做啲嘢噉囉<br />\n唔係個個國家啲當權者都知自己做緊咩"},{"pid":"ec8c7f14b1743d460906190d66d10a4a4dbc2489","tid":774781,"uid":33213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"780cec5aaebe99b3e297c6f6315a8881bbe94fdf","tid":774781,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7df328199b97c7c951506f3024cce8bbfb206eea","tid":774781,"uid":33213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08e5d4379aa81252b737f11c11124b79a2736e6a","tid":774